&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;DoiT is a global technology company that works with cloud-driven organizations to leverage the cloud to drive business growth and innovation. We combine data, technology, and human expertise to ensure our customers are operating in a well-architected and scalable state - from planning to production.&lt;/p&gt;
