&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;****Something new just launched at DoiT — and now we can talk about it.****&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Meet &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.doit.com/products/attribute&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Attribute™&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: AI tokenomics without tags, SDKs, or code changes. A lightweight eBPF sensor installs in 15 minutes and starts producing per-customer, per-feature, and per-agent token economics the same day. No instrumentation. No tagging policy. No engineering lift.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The problem it solves is real and measurable. In DoiT&#39;s&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.doit.com/what-500-finance-leaders-actually-know-about-their-ai-spend/&quot;&gt; survey of 500 finance and technology leaders&lt;/a&gt;, only 15% said they could calculate AI ROI without significant bottlenecks — and 79% experienced AI-related cost overruns in the past 12 months. AI spend is tripling. Visibility isn&#39;t keeping up. Attribute™ fixes that, at the kernel level, with nothing to instrument.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;ve established product-market fit. The early customer conversations are unusually good. Now we&#39;re building&lt;strong&gt; the founding sales team&lt;/strong&gt; to take it to market across North America and EMEA.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;ve ever wanted to be employee number something-small on a product that actually moves the category, this is that role.&lt;/p&gt;
